WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:34.505

00:01:34.505 --> 00:01:37.025
MAIN TITLE

00:03:02.145 --> 00:03:04.225
Don't blame me.
Don't blame me. Don't blame me.

00:03:48.305 --> 00:03:51.425
EPISODE TITLE

00:03:51.505 --> 00:03:57.505
XINYA FASHION, CASUAL WEAR

00:04:07.385 --> 00:04:10.585
YONG'S FASHION

00:04:20.345 --> 00:04:22.385
PERSON IN CHARGE: SUN ZHENGYONG

00:04:25.705 --> 00:04:27.345
Young man, is Mr. Sun around?

00:04:27.425 --> 00:04:28.465
I want to pick up some stock.

00:04:28.545 --> 00:04:29.465
He's gone out to restock.

00:04:30.065 --> 00:04:32.345
-When did he leave?
-No idea.

00:04:32.425 --> 00:04:34.545
If you're picking up goods,
leave your pager number.

00:04:48.145 --> 00:04:50.105
CLOSED TODAY, JUNE 30TH

00:04:50.185 --> 00:04:51.025
Young man,

00:04:51.745 --> 00:04:54.505
why is the shop closed on June 30th?

00:04:54.585 --> 00:04:55.945
No idea.

00:04:57.225 --> 00:04:58.865
Whatever I ask, you don't know.

00:04:58.945 --> 00:05:00.105
Do you work here?

00:05:00.185 --> 00:05:02.865
Mister, I only started two days ago.

00:05:02.945 --> 00:05:04.305
I haven't even seen the boss.

00:05:04.385 --> 00:05:06.265
-You've never seen him?
-No.

00:05:06.345 --> 00:05:08.425
-Where did he go?
-No idea.

00:05:09.745 --> 00:05:11.145
His wife told me

00:05:11.225 --> 00:05:12.665
to tell anyone who asks where he is
that he's out restocking.

00:05:12.745 --> 00:05:15.505
If they ask when he'll be back,
just say I don't know.

00:05:15.585 --> 00:05:17.185
So I really don't know.

00:05:30.905 --> 00:05:33.305
I'm from the Nanshan Branch.
I'm here to ask a few questions.

00:05:33.945 --> 00:05:36.065
Hello, Officer. I'm Jessica.
How can I help?

00:05:36.145 --> 00:05:37.145
JESSICA

00:05:37.225 --> 00:05:39.825
I'd like to check
the sales record for this dress.

00:05:40.585 --> 00:05:42.585
B12200Y.

00:05:42.665 --> 00:05:43.865
One moment, please.

00:05:45.145 --> 00:05:47.585
BOWLS

00:05:47.665 --> 00:05:49.465
This is one of our signature pieces.

00:05:49.545 --> 00:05:52.025
We've sold 84 pieces
since its spring launch.

00:05:52.625 --> 00:05:55.425
-Is there a customer named Sun Zhengyong?
-Let me check.

00:06:00.385 --> 00:06:03.065
Yes. Mr. Sun is our VIP client.

00:06:03.145 --> 00:06:05.945
On May 10th, he bought 11
of the same dress.

00:06:06.025 --> 00:06:07.745
Wait, no. Twelve.

00:06:07.825 --> 00:06:09.705
We gave him one as a freebie. Have a look.

00:06:10.465 --> 00:06:12.305
SALES DATE: MAY 10TH, SUN ZHENGYONG

00:06:14.545 --> 00:06:19.305
RETURNED 11 DRY-CLEANING VOUCHERS
RECEIVED ONE EXTRA DRESS

00:06:31.105 --> 00:06:32.625
Where's Captain Feng?
Didn't he want to see me?

00:06:32.705 --> 00:06:34.265
Officer He, he's in a task force meeting.

00:06:34.345 --> 00:06:35.225
He told me to wait here for you.

00:06:35.305 --> 00:06:36.545
This is Jin Manlang's statement
from this afternoon.

00:06:36.625 --> 00:06:37.625
Take a look.

00:06:37.705 --> 00:06:40.025
He denied that anyone
had hired him to kill.

00:06:40.105 --> 00:06:41.185
He claimed he only went
after Xu Meng and her dad

00:06:41.265 --> 00:06:42.265
to collect a debt.

00:06:44.065 --> 00:06:46.185
Jin Manlang has grown a pair.
He's trying to retract his confession.

00:06:46.265 --> 00:06:49.105
Officer He, there's more.
Jin Manlang said…

00:06:49.185 --> 00:06:50.985
What else did he say? Just say it.

00:06:51.785 --> 00:06:52.785
He said he's going to report you

00:06:52.865 --> 00:06:54.145
for forcing a confession.

00:06:56.785 --> 00:06:59.225
That Wolfie is unbelievable.

00:06:59.305 --> 00:07:00.505
He's pinning that on me.

00:07:00.585 --> 00:07:02.465
Bring him in. I want
to question him face-to-face.

00:07:02.545 --> 00:07:05.425
JIN MANLANG'S INTERROGATION RECORD

00:07:05.505 --> 00:07:08.065
JIN MANLANG, SECURITY DEPARTMENT
DEMOLITION DEPARTMENT

00:07:08.145 --> 00:07:09.585
LONGWEI GROUP

00:07:09.665 --> 00:07:10.505
‎2015

00:07:11.225 --> 00:07:12.345
It isn't ripe yet.

00:07:12.865 --> 00:07:14.185
Seriously.

00:07:15.145 --> 00:07:16.345
Pick another one for me.

00:07:16.425 --> 00:07:18.065
Just that one.

00:07:18.145 --> 00:07:19.065
RELOCATION BENEFITS ALL
SIGN EARLY, GAIN MORE

00:07:22.065 --> 00:07:23.905
-Give it here.
-It's not ripe. Why are you grabbing them?

00:07:23.985 --> 00:07:27.105
Come here, I said. Be in your position.

00:07:27.825 --> 00:07:28.705
Be in your position, okay?

00:07:29.625 --> 00:07:30.705
Keep your eyes peeled.

00:07:35.625 --> 00:07:36.665
Officer He.

00:07:38.025 --> 00:07:41.425
What brings you here, sir?

00:07:42.465 --> 00:07:43.585
Who are you?

00:07:45.385 --> 00:07:48.185
It's me. Lang. Lang.

00:07:49.705 --> 00:07:51.065
JIN MANLANG, SECURITY DEPARTMENT
DEMOLITION DEPARTMENT

00:07:52.785 --> 00:07:53.745
Look at you all cleaned up.

00:07:53.825 --> 00:07:55.705
You're a security manager now, huh?

00:07:55.785 --> 00:07:58.345
What? Running forced demolitions?

00:07:58.865 --> 00:08:00.025
No way.

00:08:00.865 --> 00:08:03.305
We keep things civil.

00:08:03.385 --> 00:08:05.145
We don't do dirty tricks.

00:08:05.225 --> 00:08:07.585
-What brings you here, Officer He?
-I'm here to observe.

00:08:09.065 --> 00:08:11.065
Right this way. Please come in.

00:08:15.465 --> 00:08:16.665
Welcome.

00:08:28.225 --> 00:08:29.145
Everyone,

00:08:29.665 --> 00:08:32.225
please let me go over this again.

00:08:32.305 --> 00:08:35.505
Longwei Group's compensation standards

00:08:35.585 --> 00:08:36.585
have always been consistent.

00:08:36.664 --> 00:08:37.825
Whether you move in early or late…

00:08:37.904 --> 00:08:39.865
Didn't someone say they'd
never come, no matter what?

00:08:40.465 --> 00:08:44.545
Now, you can take a look
at the notice in your hands.

00:08:44.625 --> 00:08:48.025
If you have any questions or doubts,

00:08:48.105 --> 00:08:50.145
come see me at the Redevelopment Bureau.

00:08:50.225 --> 00:08:51.145
My name is Qiao Suqing.

00:08:51.225 --> 00:08:52.105
Feng,

00:08:52.625 --> 00:08:55.945
doesn't that woman on stage look familiar?

00:08:56.025 --> 00:08:58.945
Wasn't she the mistress
from the fourth floor?

00:09:00.545 --> 00:09:02.705
Don't believe Du's nonsense.

00:09:02.785 --> 00:09:04.905
Qiao is a decent woman.

00:09:04.985 --> 00:09:07.145
She's now the finance director
at Longwei Real Estate.

00:09:07.825 --> 00:09:10.625
She's in charge of Yuanlongli's
demolition project.

00:09:10.705 --> 00:09:14.625
Also, if any household needs help moving,

00:09:14.705 --> 00:09:16.945
we'll do what we can to assist.

00:09:18.385 --> 00:09:20.225
The relocation service is a trap.

00:09:20.305 --> 00:09:21.305
Don't fall for it.

00:09:21.385 --> 00:09:24.145
QIAO SUQING

00:09:24.225 --> 00:09:25.425
Even a few hundred yuan would be too much.

00:09:48.425 --> 00:09:49.505
I can't talk him into it.

00:09:49.585 --> 00:09:51.345
Qiao, you're not an outsider here.

00:09:51.425 --> 00:09:53.265
You tell me. Should he stay or not?

00:09:56.665 --> 00:09:57.545
Mr. He,

00:09:57.625 --> 00:09:59.745
if even you can't convince him,

00:09:59.825 --> 00:10:01.465
I'm not in a position to say anything.

00:10:01.545 --> 00:10:03.225
Why not?

00:10:03.305 --> 00:10:05.265
He won't listen to me,

00:10:05.345 --> 00:10:06.745
but he might listen to you.

00:10:20.505 --> 00:10:21.625
You don't have to say it.

00:10:21.705 --> 00:10:23.825
I can tell from your eyes.

00:10:23.905 --> 00:10:25.585
You want him to stay.

00:10:28.905 --> 00:10:31.385
She's made herself pretty clear.

00:10:31.465 --> 00:10:32.825
Say something.

00:10:32.905 --> 00:10:35.545
Sir, don't put her on the spot.

00:10:35.625 --> 00:10:37.025
I'm definitely going back to Beijing.

00:10:37.105 --> 00:10:38.145
I have classes.

00:10:38.225 --> 00:10:40.345
You're the one
putting her in a tough spot.

00:10:40.945 --> 00:10:42.865
She wants you to stay.

00:10:42.945 --> 00:10:44.945
Don't play dumb.

00:10:58.105 --> 00:10:59.265
Mr. He,

00:11:00.785 --> 00:11:02.465
it's been so long.

00:11:04.305 --> 00:11:05.465
It's time

00:11:06.225 --> 00:11:07.145
to let go.

00:11:12.225 --> 00:11:14.545
You should let Ran go.

00:11:18.185 --> 00:11:20.305
What's wrong with you?
Why won't you ever say what you mean?

00:11:20.905 --> 00:11:22.185
-You clearly…
-Sir,

00:11:22.705 --> 00:11:24.105
just listen to her.

00:11:27.465 --> 00:11:29.825
Ran Fangxu, as your mentor,

00:11:29.905 --> 00:11:32.625
I'm ordering you to stay in Weiyang.

00:11:40.145 --> 00:11:42.185
TRAIN TICKET: WEIYANG TO BEIJING

00:11:42.265 --> 00:11:43.225
This is a ticket back to Beijing

00:11:44.465 --> 00:11:45.425
for tomorrow morning.

00:11:54.665 --> 00:11:55.905
Trying to walk back his own confession?

00:11:55.985 --> 00:11:56.825
‎1997

00:12:00.265 --> 00:12:04.345
SUN BOUGHT THE DRESS
I'LL CHECK THE CCTV IN YUANLONGLI. RAN

00:12:08.705 --> 00:12:10.705
When one door closes, another opens.

00:12:10.785 --> 00:12:12.505
There's always a way through.

00:12:15.665 --> 00:12:16.585
Captain Feng.

00:12:18.225 --> 00:12:20.305
Officer He, great job.

00:12:21.105 --> 00:12:23.825
You actually let the suspect
turn the tables on you.

00:12:25.425 --> 00:12:26.865
Let him make the noise for now.

00:12:26.945 --> 00:12:28.585
I'll have them list
everything out soon enough.

00:12:28.665 --> 00:12:29.505
No need to wait.

00:12:29.585 --> 00:12:31.785
Later, head to HR

00:12:31.865 --> 00:12:33.145
and process your transfer back.

00:12:33.225 --> 00:12:35.665
Also, get Ran over here.

00:12:35.745 --> 00:12:36.985
We're short-handed here.

00:12:39.145 --> 00:12:40.905
Captain Feng, don't.

00:12:42.105 --> 00:12:43.945
There's still one day left.

00:12:48.265 --> 00:12:50.665
You're the leader.
You have to keep your word.

00:12:50.745 --> 00:12:53.065
What can you do in one day?

00:12:53.145 --> 00:12:54.745
That's barely enough
for you to make a fuss about.

00:12:54.825 --> 00:12:57.305
Alright. Enough messing around.

00:12:57.385 --> 00:12:58.265
Get out of my sight.

00:12:58.865 --> 00:13:02.185
Captain Feng, I know
you're not really fed up with me.

00:13:02.265 --> 00:13:05.145
You're just annoyed
about that mining case.

00:13:05.225 --> 00:13:08.065
By the way, Ran brought in
a pickpocket yesterday.

00:13:08.145 --> 00:13:09.305
That guy, Luandongzi.

00:13:09.385 --> 00:13:11.865
The task force should follow up on him.

00:13:16.025 --> 00:13:17.225
-A pickpocket?
-Yeah.

00:13:17.305 --> 00:13:19.225
Ask if he's stashed a briefcase

00:13:19.305 --> 00:13:20.705
with "Qingsong Cement" on it.

00:13:20.785 --> 00:13:22.265
There's an important document inside.

00:13:22.345 --> 00:13:24.505
-That might be useful.
-He Yuanhang.

00:13:24.585 --> 00:13:27.865
Wait. What are you talking about?
What briefcase?

00:13:27.945 --> 00:13:29.665
He Yuanhang. Get back here!

00:13:59.625 --> 00:14:01.225
Sun Zhengyong isn't at the shop.

00:14:01.945 --> 00:14:04.785
But I did find something. On June 30th,
he suddenly shut the place down.

00:14:04.865 --> 00:14:06.905
That alone puts him on our radar.

00:14:06.985 --> 00:14:08.985
Mm. I'm pulling the CCTV from the 30th

00:14:09.065 --> 00:14:11.385
to check if he showed up
at Yuanlongli that day.

00:14:11.465 --> 00:14:13.385
Leave no stone unturned.

00:14:13.905 --> 00:14:14.945
Xinglong.

00:14:15.025 --> 00:14:16.385
Get me all the footage
from before the 30th.

00:14:17.665 --> 00:14:18.825
Got it.

00:14:20.865 --> 00:14:21.705
I'll make a call.

00:14:29.265 --> 00:14:31.865
-Hello?
-Hello? Qiao?

00:14:31.945 --> 00:14:34.185
-Officer He.
-Speaking.

00:14:34.265 --> 00:14:37.185
-Xiaohe's asleep.
-She's asleep?

00:14:37.265 --> 00:14:38.425
How about this?

00:14:38.505 --> 00:14:40.825
Could you let her stay
the night at your place?

00:14:40.905 --> 00:14:42.745
I'll have her grandma
pick her up tomorrow.

00:14:42.825 --> 00:14:43.865
Of course.

00:14:44.465 --> 00:14:47.625
Officer He, no need
to trouble her grandma.

00:14:47.705 --> 00:14:50.385
If you're fine with it,
give me the address.

00:14:50.465 --> 00:14:51.825
I'll send her there in the morning.

00:14:51.905 --> 00:14:54.185
I'm totally fine with it. Of course.

00:14:54.265 --> 00:14:56.785
Write this down. The address
is 102, Building Unit 2,

00:14:56.865 --> 00:14:58.425
Happiness Garden.

00:14:58.505 --> 00:15:00.505
Well, sorry to trouble you again.

00:15:00.585 --> 00:15:02.105
Not at all.

00:15:02.185 --> 00:15:04.825
Alright, I've got the address.

00:15:04.905 --> 00:15:07.305
I'll bring Xiaohe over
after breakfast tomorrow.

00:15:07.385 --> 00:15:09.385
-Sure. Thank you.
-No problem.

00:15:09.465 --> 00:15:10.305
I'll hang up now.

00:15:11.785 --> 00:15:13.985
I didn't know much about Qiao before.

00:15:14.985 --> 00:15:18.825
But she's really thoughtful

00:15:18.905 --> 00:15:20.585
and knows how to carry herself.

00:15:27.705 --> 00:15:29.345
There are only two people
breathing in this room.

00:15:29.425 --> 00:15:30.265
Don't pretend you didn't hear that.

00:15:31.905 --> 00:15:34.105
I heard you. Go on.

00:15:35.585 --> 00:15:36.865
Yuanlongli

00:15:36.945 --> 00:15:39.945
is either spreading superstitious nonsense
or making up rumors.

00:15:40.025 --> 00:15:42.345
Qiao is a decent person.

00:15:43.185 --> 00:15:44.825
How could they smear her as a mistress?

00:15:45.465 --> 00:15:47.305
They've gone too far. That's bullying.

00:15:47.385 --> 00:15:48.665
When I get the time,

00:15:48.745 --> 00:15:51.585
I'm going to clean up this toxic mess.

00:15:52.745 --> 00:15:54.065
Yeah, someone has to do that.

00:16:16.025 --> 00:16:18.145
Are you bringing in a video store here?

00:16:18.225 --> 00:16:19.865
Didn't you say you wanted everything?

00:16:21.145 --> 00:16:23.265
The footage from the past two weeks
is all here.

00:16:25.665 --> 00:16:26.785
Take your time.

00:16:39.145 --> 00:16:42.065
Xinglong, stop reading papers at night.

00:16:42.145 --> 00:16:43.065
You'll ruin your eyes.

00:16:43.825 --> 00:16:45.865
-Oh yeah?
-Let me ask you something.

00:16:49.385 --> 00:16:51.465
We're looking for this guy.

00:16:51.545 --> 00:16:52.425
Rat-faced.

00:16:53.225 --> 00:16:55.425
-Do you recognize him?
-No.

00:16:57.305 --> 00:16:58.425
That's fine.

00:16:58.505 --> 00:17:00.865
You can help us out.
Keep an eye out for him.

00:17:00.945 --> 00:17:02.505
Give your eyes a break too.

00:17:03.145 --> 00:17:05.145
You call this a break?

00:17:05.985 --> 00:17:07.785
Hey. I'm on duty here.

00:17:09.424 --> 00:17:11.224
There's a reward if you find him.

00:17:13.025 --> 00:17:14.585
Then I'll help.

00:17:17.265 --> 00:17:18.184
Come.

00:17:21.464 --> 00:17:22.704
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:17:34.625 --> 00:17:36.585
If you spot anyone familiar
or suspicious, call me right away.

00:17:37.545 --> 00:17:38.585
Got it.

00:17:39.745 --> 00:17:40.945
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:18:04.305 --> 00:18:07.065
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:18:26.785 --> 00:18:28.785
No. No. My eyes are going blurry.

00:18:29.305 --> 00:18:31.105
I need to go out and get some air.

00:18:31.185 --> 00:18:32.425
My eyes are shot too.

00:18:33.145 --> 00:18:34.785
You're young. How could your eyes be shot?

00:18:34.865 --> 00:18:36.985
-Keep watching.
-Everything's blurry.

00:18:37.745 --> 00:18:38.585
Keep watching.

00:18:38.665 --> 00:18:41.585
If it gets that bad,
have Officer Ran buy you some lamb liver.

00:18:41.665 --> 00:18:42.785
They're good for the eyes.

00:18:48.705 --> 00:18:49.665
He.

00:18:51.065 --> 00:18:52.825
What's wrong? Are your eyes blurry too?

00:18:52.905 --> 00:18:54.025
It's not that. Look.

00:18:58.865 --> 00:19:01.025
Got him? Which day?

00:19:01.105 --> 00:19:04.225
June 27th. 1:23 p.m.

00:19:04.305 --> 00:19:06.065
That lines up. Everything lines up.

00:19:06.145 --> 00:19:08.025
On the 27th, Sun Zhengyong

00:19:08.105 --> 00:19:10.185
scoped out the Qihuang Clinic
on the 17th floor.

00:19:10.265 --> 00:19:11.625
He found out it had shut down.

00:19:11.705 --> 00:19:12.945
Then he tricked Xu Meng

00:19:13.025 --> 00:19:14.585
into bringing her dad there
for treatment on the 30th.

00:19:14.665 --> 00:19:16.065
After that, he tipped off the person

00:19:16.145 --> 00:19:19.745
who hired Wolfie
and set him up to take the fall.

00:19:19.825 --> 00:19:21.065
Meanwhile, he hid in the building

00:19:21.145 --> 00:19:22.945
and waited for his chance
to move in on Xu Meng and her dad.

00:19:23.025 --> 00:19:24.385
It all checks out.

00:19:28.065 --> 00:19:31.825
But Xu Meng and her dad
took the elevator to the 18th floor.

00:19:31.905 --> 00:19:33.225
How did he know that in advance?

00:19:33.305 --> 00:19:34.865
Isn't that obvious?

00:19:34.945 --> 00:19:37.905
He told Xu Meng the clinic
had moved to the 18th floor.

00:19:40.225 --> 00:19:42.705
Then how did he wipe his tracks?

00:19:43.465 --> 00:19:45.385
Why are you back
to playing "20 Questions"?

00:19:45.465 --> 00:19:47.185
I'll track down his address right now,

00:19:47.265 --> 00:19:49.705
drag him in front of you,
and let him explain it himself.

00:19:49.785 --> 00:19:50.625
Wait for me.

00:19:53.345 --> 00:19:54.745
If I can't find him, I…

00:19:54.825 --> 00:19:55.985
Wait. Hold on.

00:19:57.105 --> 00:19:59.265
Ran. He. It's him.

00:19:59.945 --> 00:20:00.865
I… It's him!

00:20:01.465 --> 00:20:03.025
That rat-faced guy.

00:20:05.905 --> 00:20:07.345
Which day's footage is this?

00:20:07.425 --> 00:20:08.585
This isn't footage.

00:20:08.665 --> 00:20:10.185
It's live.

00:20:13.705 --> 00:20:14.505
Quick.

00:20:14.585 --> 00:20:15.745
-Quick.
-Let's go.

00:20:18.985 --> 00:20:20.545
-Seventeenth floor. Seventeenth.
-No.

00:20:21.305 --> 00:20:23.665
Get off at 16th. Hit both elevators
down to the first floor,

00:20:23.745 --> 00:20:25.145
then take the stairs up to the 17th.

00:20:25.225 --> 00:20:26.505
We box him in from two sides.

00:20:28.465 --> 00:20:31.585
He, you're indeed an expert
in making arrests on-site.

00:20:32.905 --> 00:20:35.225
You still have a lot more
to learn. Alright?

00:20:35.305 --> 00:20:37.025
But I don't get it.

00:20:37.105 --> 00:20:39.545
What's he doing back
at Yuanlongli right now?

00:20:40.625 --> 00:20:42.185
I read this somewhere.

00:20:42.265 --> 00:20:45.545
Murderers and lovers
tend to revisit the scene.

00:20:45.625 --> 00:20:46.465
I didn't know that.

00:20:47.745 --> 00:20:49.105
You still have a lot more to learn.

00:21:04.025 --> 00:21:07.465
QIHUANG CLINIC

00:21:16.865 --> 00:21:17.905
Sun Zhengyong.

00:21:19.945 --> 00:21:21.025
Police.

00:21:21.545 --> 00:21:24.505
Stop. Ran, he's heading your way.

00:21:41.225 --> 00:21:42.225
Ran Fangxu,

00:21:42.745 --> 00:21:45.745
taking down suspects
is basic police training.

00:21:45.825 --> 00:21:47.585
You need to get past this.

00:21:47.665 --> 00:21:48.825
What?

00:21:55.985 --> 00:21:58.065
How did you pass
your physical training test?

00:21:59.465 --> 00:22:01.785
Shut up. Steady your breathing.
Face him head-on.

00:22:06.985 --> 00:22:09.345
Horse stance. Turn into a side lunge.
Block. Trip him.

00:22:11.985 --> 00:22:14.465
Shout. Feint a punch.
Knee strike to the abdomen.

00:22:26.385 --> 00:22:27.185
Got him.

00:22:31.825 --> 00:22:32.865
Still trying to run?

00:22:34.065 --> 00:22:36.665
He, thanks for the coaching.

00:22:37.945 --> 00:22:38.825
Have some faith.

00:22:39.865 --> 00:22:40.705
Are you okay?

00:22:43.185 --> 00:22:48.305
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

00:22:48.385 --> 00:22:49.305
MIRROR

00:22:50.305 --> 00:22:51.585
-Over here.
-Move.

00:22:59.425 --> 00:23:01.105
-Captain Feng.
-Captain Feng.

00:23:03.425 --> 00:23:04.505
Did you crack the case?

00:23:05.185 --> 00:23:06.025
We still need to interrogate him.

00:23:09.305 --> 00:23:10.225
Upstairs.

00:23:22.705 --> 00:23:23.745
Sun Zhengyong,

00:23:24.945 --> 00:23:26.265
let's not waste time.

00:23:26.345 --> 00:23:27.305
Where's Xu Meng?

00:23:27.905 --> 00:23:28.745
Xu Meng?

00:23:32.825 --> 00:23:34.745
Do you mean Mengmeng?

00:23:34.825 --> 00:23:36.105
Where's Mengmeng?

00:23:36.185 --> 00:23:37.865
She took her dad and left.

00:23:37.945 --> 00:23:40.145
They bought train tickets for July 1st.

00:23:43.505 --> 00:23:44.865
Did you see them leave?

00:23:44.945 --> 00:23:45.905
No.

00:23:45.985 --> 00:23:48.385
One day, she came to me

00:23:49.065 --> 00:23:50.265
and asked to borrow some money.

00:23:50.345 --> 00:23:51.385
When?

00:23:51.465 --> 00:23:54.105
Around late June.

00:23:55.305 --> 00:23:58.145
She said someone was threatening her
and wanted her dead.

00:23:58.665 --> 00:24:01.265
So she planned to take her dad
and get out of here for good.

00:24:01.345 --> 00:24:02.745
But she was worried

00:24:02.825 --> 00:24:04.705
the trip would be too much for her dad.

00:24:05.305 --> 00:24:09.305
So before leaving, she wanted
to take him to Qihuang Clinic for therapy.

00:24:09.905 --> 00:24:11.825
She sounded so pitiful.

00:24:12.345 --> 00:24:13.665
I lent her 30,000.

00:24:13.745 --> 00:24:15.145
I didn't expect her

00:24:15.225 --> 00:24:17.945
to disappear right after taking the money.

00:24:20.465 --> 00:24:22.305
Where did you hide them?

00:24:22.385 --> 00:24:23.945
I didn't.

00:24:26.985 --> 00:24:29.065
Officer, did something happen

00:24:29.665 --> 00:24:31.185
to Mengmeng?

00:24:32.185 --> 00:24:34.185
You lent her that much money.

00:24:34.265 --> 00:24:35.505
What's your relationship?

00:24:36.385 --> 00:24:37.545
I like her.

00:24:37.625 --> 00:24:39.145
How do you like her?

00:24:39.745 --> 00:24:43.145
You know what she does for a living.

00:24:43.985 --> 00:24:46.025
I'd book her all the time.

00:24:46.105 --> 00:24:48.625
One day, I got drunk.

00:24:48.705 --> 00:24:50.465
I told her I wanted to go out with her.

00:24:50.985 --> 00:24:54.105
She thought I was talking nonsense
and turned me down.

00:24:54.185 --> 00:24:57.185
I was mad. We got into an argument.

00:24:57.265 --> 00:24:58.705
And then you forced yourself on her?

00:24:58.785 --> 00:25:00.345
No, I didn't. No.

00:25:00.425 --> 00:25:03.305
-Did you buy Xu Meng clothes?
-Yeah.

00:25:04.505 --> 00:25:06.065
Did you give her a dress from Bowls?

00:25:06.145 --> 00:25:08.185
Bowls?

00:25:11.185 --> 00:25:12.585
Maybe.

00:25:13.465 --> 00:25:15.465
I often go to malls.

00:25:15.545 --> 00:25:19.585
When big brands go on sale, I stock up.

00:25:19.665 --> 00:25:22.025
First, it makes good gifts for girls.

00:25:22.105 --> 00:25:24.185
Second, I can copy the design

00:25:24.785 --> 00:25:26.345
and get my money back.

00:25:28.945 --> 00:25:30.065
Sun Zhengyong,

00:25:30.985 --> 00:25:32.025
you can spin tall tales.

00:25:32.105 --> 00:25:35.025
No matter how well you spin it,
it's still a story.

00:25:35.105 --> 00:25:36.345
Tell me.

00:25:36.425 --> 00:25:39.185
Why did you suddenly
shut your shop on the 30th?

00:25:39.265 --> 00:25:43.105
And why were you on the 17th floor
of New York Block on the 27th?

00:25:43.945 --> 00:25:45.385
Then this morning,

00:25:45.465 --> 00:25:47.425
you went back to No. 1713 again.

00:25:47.505 --> 00:25:48.865
And you ran when you saw us.

00:25:48.945 --> 00:25:51.465
Try making up a story for all that.

00:25:56.265 --> 00:25:57.225
Feeling guilty?

00:25:58.305 --> 00:25:59.425
Go on.

00:25:59.945 --> 00:26:01.985
I have plenty more evidence
to help you fill in the blanks.

00:26:02.065 --> 00:26:03.025
I…

00:26:03.785 --> 00:26:04.905
I can't hold it anymore.

00:26:04.985 --> 00:26:07.585
Then talk. Where's Xu Meng?

00:26:07.665 --> 00:26:08.905
That's not what I meant.

00:26:09.745 --> 00:26:11.105
I need the bathroom.

00:26:11.825 --> 00:26:13.945
I have prostate issues.

00:26:14.025 --> 00:26:15.385
I can't hold it in.

00:26:15.465 --> 00:26:19.105
And just now, this officer kicked me.

00:26:19.185 --> 00:26:21.425
I really can't take it anymore.

00:26:25.625 --> 00:26:27.505
I'm about to burst.

00:26:31.625 --> 00:26:34.625
DUTY AND SELF-RESTRAINT
RIGHTEOUSNESS AND PEACE

00:26:34.705 --> 00:26:35.545
Look who it is.

00:26:35.625 --> 00:26:37.465
The famous Officer He.

00:26:38.185 --> 00:26:39.465
Still with the Criminal Department?

00:26:39.545 --> 00:26:40.985
Not coming back?

00:26:41.065 --> 00:26:42.985
Of course. This is
where the big cases are.

00:26:43.065 --> 00:26:46.705
Unlike someone who couldn't
even handle public order.

00:26:46.785 --> 00:26:47.905
Keep bragging. Go on.

00:26:47.985 --> 00:26:49.265
Big cases? How big?

00:26:49.345 --> 00:26:50.585
Bigger than a task force case?

00:26:50.665 --> 00:26:52.705
Do you have to give proper case briefings?

00:26:52.785 --> 00:26:54.625
You're just someone
stringing up police tape,

00:26:54.705 --> 00:26:55.945
and now you're talking
task force briefings?

00:26:56.025 --> 00:26:57.505
You sure have a knack
for blowing your own trumpet.

00:26:57.585 --> 00:26:58.585
And you're any better?

00:26:58.665 --> 00:27:00.785
Still chasing that prank case, aren't you?

00:27:00.865 --> 00:27:02.585
Come on. Let me see.
What big suspect did you catch?

00:27:04.505 --> 00:27:05.625
Officer Qu.

00:27:06.385 --> 00:27:08.745
He Yuanhang, are you trying to amuse me?

00:27:09.585 --> 00:27:11.025
A criminal investigator like you

00:27:11.105 --> 00:27:12.825
is actually busting
a street vendor selling fakes?

00:27:14.985 --> 00:27:16.705
Officer Qu, do you know this guy?

00:27:17.305 --> 00:27:18.545
He's Mr. Sun.

00:27:18.625 --> 00:27:21.185
He shows up at the station twice a week.

00:27:21.265 --> 00:27:22.345
Busier than Officer He.

00:27:23.385 --> 00:27:24.225
A week?

00:27:24.305 --> 00:27:26.545
-When was he brought in?
-Last week.

00:27:27.185 --> 00:27:28.465
June 29th.

00:27:28.545 --> 00:27:30.745
He was selling counterfeit goods
and got into a fight.

00:27:30.825 --> 00:27:32.905
He was brought in and held for five days.

00:27:39.425 --> 00:27:42.785
You suspect he has something to do
with that prank case?

00:27:45.425 --> 00:27:47.905
I can vouch for him. It wasn't him.

00:27:48.505 --> 00:27:49.425
He didn't have the time.

00:27:58.705 --> 00:28:03.065
Officer, if I don't go now,
I'm going to piss myself.

00:28:06.105 --> 00:28:09.505
DUTY AND SELF-RESTRAINT
RIGHTEOUSNESS AND PEACE

00:28:16.625 --> 00:28:17.785
Officer,

00:28:18.425 --> 00:28:20.265
about the first question from earlier,

00:28:20.345 --> 00:28:22.025
you already know the answer.

00:28:22.105 --> 00:28:25.385
Now I'll answer the second and third.

00:28:25.465 --> 00:28:29.145
I ran when I saw you because I panicked.

00:28:29.225 --> 00:28:32.105
I thought you were after
my counterfeit business.

00:28:32.185 --> 00:28:34.585
As for the 17th floor at New York Block,

00:28:34.665 --> 00:28:37.905
there's a tailor there I work with.

00:28:37.985 --> 00:28:40.705
Last week, I took the fabric
to make samples.

00:28:41.305 --> 00:28:43.985
This morning, I went to collect
the finished goods.

00:28:44.065 --> 00:28:46.065
But when I got to the 17th,

00:28:46.145 --> 00:28:49.345
I didn't know why, something just hit me.

00:28:49.425 --> 00:28:50.625
I suddenly thought of Mengmeng.

00:28:51.465 --> 00:28:53.865
So I figured I'd check out Qihuang Clinic.

00:28:53.945 --> 00:28:57.825
I didn't know it had shut down.

00:28:57.905 --> 00:29:00.225
Mengmeng played me.

00:29:00.305 --> 00:29:02.425
That's enough. You don't need to go on.

00:29:03.065 --> 00:29:07.145
You really shouldn't
get too close to unlucky people.

00:29:07.225 --> 00:29:09.465
Bad luck spreads like a disease.

00:29:09.545 --> 00:29:11.305
Once it sticks, it rubs off.

00:29:13.465 --> 00:29:17.105
Officer, did Mengmeng go missing?

00:29:18.345 --> 00:29:20.425
That might be the best outcome

00:29:20.945 --> 00:29:22.585
for the people around her.

00:29:22.665 --> 00:29:25.105
Enough said. Spare me the act.

00:29:25.185 --> 00:29:26.265
You're no saint yourself.

00:29:26.345 --> 00:29:27.545
You're too rotten
for bad luck to touch you.

00:29:30.225 --> 00:29:31.345
Can you take these off now?

00:29:54.065 --> 00:29:55.945
-Mr. Song.
-What is it?

00:29:56.025 --> 00:29:57.425
Cripple Du's men were tailing me.

00:29:57.505 --> 00:29:59.025
Just as I dug the body up,

00:29:59.105 --> 00:30:01.625
they snatched it and took my car.

00:30:02.985 --> 00:30:05.545
-What did you just say?
-I'm telling the truth.

00:30:05.625 --> 00:30:07.785
Look at this. My head
has been thrashed badly.

00:30:30.665 --> 00:30:31.505
Who sent this over?

00:30:43.025 --> 00:30:44.505
-Who?
-Song Qingsong,

00:30:45.465 --> 00:30:46.865
did you see the photo?

00:30:48.345 --> 00:30:51.025
Director Li, what photo? I have no idea.

00:30:51.105 --> 00:30:52.905
Stop pretending.

00:30:52.985 --> 00:30:55.385
That photo was left right at my doorstep.

00:30:56.505 --> 00:30:57.385
Song Qingsong,

00:30:57.905 --> 00:30:59.545
I don't care if you make dirty money.

00:31:00.385 --> 00:31:02.065
But you actually killed someone.

00:31:03.665 --> 00:31:05.545
Director Li, hear me out.

00:31:05.625 --> 00:31:07.585
Someone has died! Hear you out for what?

00:31:08.385 --> 00:31:10.945
Listen carefully. Go on the run.

00:31:11.025 --> 00:31:12.705
-Right now.
-Alright. Drop the act.

00:31:12.785 --> 00:31:13.825
What did you say?

00:31:14.505 --> 00:31:16.465
Did you get Cripple Du to take my car

00:31:17.305 --> 00:31:19.025
and have someone seal the bid document?

00:31:19.105 --> 00:31:20.465
Song Qingsong.

00:31:20.985 --> 00:31:21.745
-I…
-Li.

00:31:21.825 --> 00:31:23.505
Listen up.

00:31:23.585 --> 00:31:25.865
I didn't burn the bid you sold me.

00:31:25.945 --> 00:31:27.145
So here are your options.

00:31:27.225 --> 00:31:31.625
One, I keep Dongshan Mine
and you tell Cripple Du to get lost.

00:31:32.265 --> 00:31:34.065
Second, you return the eight million.

00:31:34.145 --> 00:31:36.065
Otherwise, we both go down together.

00:31:36.145 --> 00:31:37.745
We all go down together!

00:31:37.825 --> 00:31:39.385
Song Qingsong,

00:31:39.465 --> 00:31:42.065
between bribery and murder,
which one carries the heavier sentence?

00:31:42.145 --> 00:31:43.585
We're not going down together.

00:31:43.665 --> 00:31:45.105
I'm not scared!

00:31:45.185 --> 00:31:46.385
I have money.

00:31:46.465 --> 00:31:48.305
I could kill more and still
find someone to take the fall.

00:31:48.385 --> 00:31:50.745
What can you do to me? What can you do?

00:31:57.705 --> 00:32:00.465
I'm not scared! I have money.

00:32:00.545 --> 00:32:02.465
I could kill more and still
find someone to take the fall.

00:32:02.545 --> 00:32:05.705
What can you do to me? What can you do?

00:32:07.665 --> 00:32:10.265
I'm not scared! I have money.

00:32:10.345 --> 00:32:12.025
I could kill more and still
find someone to take the fall.

00:32:12.105 --> 00:32:14.425
What can you do to me? What can you do?

00:32:15.705 --> 00:32:17.105
Song Qingsong,

00:32:17.625 --> 00:32:20.465
you're not just ignorant of the law,
you are stupid.

00:32:20.545 --> 00:32:21.385
Son of a bitch.

00:32:21.465 --> 00:32:23.145
You are despicable.

00:32:23.665 --> 00:32:25.865
Now I'll give you two options.

00:32:25.945 --> 00:32:27.185
One, I burn the photo,

00:32:27.865 --> 00:32:28.825
you go out and lie low for a while.

00:32:29.425 --> 00:32:33.105
Two, I hand the photo and the recording
over to the police.

00:32:33.625 --> 00:32:36.985
Keep both your money and your life
or lose everything. Your call.

00:32:39.265 --> 00:32:41.465
Mr… Mr. Song. Mr. Song. Mr. Song.

00:32:41.545 --> 00:32:44.265
I was wrong. Mr. Song. Forgive me.

00:32:44.785 --> 00:32:47.105
-It's my fault.
-All of you

00:32:47.905 --> 00:32:49.505
are trying to screw me over.

00:32:49.585 --> 00:32:51.585
Mr. Song. Forgive me.

00:33:23.585 --> 00:33:25.385
WEIYANG CITY DONGSHAN MINE BID DOCUMENT

00:33:36.265 --> 00:33:38.105
Book me two tickets to Los Angeles.

00:33:38.985 --> 00:33:40.145
As soon as possible.

00:33:40.785 --> 00:33:42.985
Got it, Mr. Song. Who's going with you?

00:33:51.425 --> 00:33:54.225
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

00:33:56.705 --> 00:33:59.545
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY

00:34:10.185 --> 00:34:12.344
Mr. Song. Cripple Du's men are here.

00:34:14.025 --> 00:34:14.865
Go.

00:34:17.505 --> 00:34:19.065
‎-Stop!
‎-Don't run!

00:34:19.145 --> 00:34:20.784
‎-Stay there!
‎-Don't run!

00:34:27.945 --> 00:34:29.304
Qingsong. Take the back door.

00:34:29.385 --> 00:34:30.344
We leave together.

00:34:30.425 --> 00:34:32.465
Too late. We don't have time. Qingsong.

00:34:32.545 --> 00:34:34.385
Don't worry, Qingsong.
The police won't trace it here.

00:34:34.465 --> 00:34:37.145
Even if they do,
I'll take the fall. Go now.

00:34:38.344 --> 00:34:40.225
As long as you, my sister,
and your child are safe,

00:34:40.304 --> 00:34:41.784
even if I take a bullet for it,

00:34:41.865 --> 00:34:43.145
it'll be worth it.

00:34:43.225 --> 00:34:46.425
Shanlong, after I'm gone,
you're the factory director.

00:34:47.025 --> 00:34:48.344
Take care of everything for me.

00:34:48.945 --> 00:34:51.505
-Qingsong, go. Qingsong, go.
-I'll be back.

00:34:51.585 --> 00:34:53.105
-I'll be back.
-Go, Qingsong.

00:34:53.185 --> 00:34:55.025
Qingsong, go.

00:34:58.625 --> 00:34:59.745
‎Fucking hell!

00:35:07.305 --> 00:35:09.825
Stop! Stop! Stop!

00:35:23.745 --> 00:35:25.825
I paid you to put on a show.

00:35:26.345 --> 00:35:28.225
You're actually beating me?

00:35:28.305 --> 00:35:31.625
For real? How dare you!

00:35:31.705 --> 00:35:32.665
Fuck.

00:35:32.745 --> 00:35:34.585
Motherfuckers.

00:35:37.065 --> 00:35:38.505
Can you be professional?

00:36:23.585 --> 00:36:25.145
You got lucky this time.

00:36:25.905 --> 00:36:28.145
It's not going to happen a third time.

00:36:48.185 --> 00:36:53.345
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

00:36:53.425 --> 00:36:55.985
INTERROGATION ROOM

00:37:02.705 --> 00:37:04.505
I was trying to prove myself.

00:37:04.585 --> 00:37:05.785
But then,

00:37:06.465 --> 00:37:08.265
I proved I was a fool.

00:37:11.145 --> 00:37:13.665
Now our only lead is Song Qingsong.

00:37:15.905 --> 00:37:18.905
-Let's go.
-Hurry up. Quit dragging your feet.

00:37:19.585 --> 00:37:21.545
Officer, my leg hurts.

00:37:21.625 --> 00:37:22.705
Wu Shanlong?

00:37:23.625 --> 00:37:26.505
FAIR AND JUST

00:37:27.665 --> 00:37:28.945
Good day, officers.

00:37:29.705 --> 00:37:31.705
-What's he in for?
-It's a misunderstanding.

00:37:32.225 --> 00:37:34.105
-Misunderstanding.
-Did they ask you?

00:37:35.385 --> 00:37:38.505
It's about Dongshan Mine.
We'll need to question him further.

00:37:38.585 --> 00:37:39.705
Have you arrested Song Qingsong?

00:37:39.785 --> 00:37:41.025
Reporting, sir.

00:37:41.785 --> 00:37:42.745
From now on,

00:37:42.825 --> 00:37:45.025
there'll be no more
Song Qingsong in Weiyang.

00:37:45.105 --> 00:37:46.305
End of report.

00:37:48.185 --> 00:37:49.185
Move.

00:38:00.065 --> 00:38:04.105
RUICHUAN RESTAURANT

00:38:05.585 --> 00:38:07.145
One faked you out,

00:38:07.665 --> 00:38:08.905
the other got away.

00:38:09.785 --> 00:38:13.105
These two are cunning.

00:38:14.385 --> 00:38:15.425
Stop reading.

00:38:16.025 --> 00:38:16.865
He got away.

00:38:16.945 --> 00:38:18.505
What's the point of staring
at the notebook?

00:38:18.585 --> 00:38:19.665
Eat the noodles. Come on.

00:38:24.545 --> 00:38:25.905
Stop reading.

00:38:25.985 --> 00:38:27.185
Listen.

00:38:27.265 --> 00:38:29.145
We're putting this case on hold for now.

00:38:29.225 --> 00:38:31.345
I've talked to Captain Feng.

00:38:31.425 --> 00:38:32.465
After this meal,

00:38:32.545 --> 00:38:34.105
you report to the Task Force.

00:38:34.185 --> 00:38:35.185
As for me,

00:38:35.945 --> 00:38:37.305
I'm going back to the station.

00:38:54.345 --> 00:38:55.265
He,

00:38:56.625 --> 00:38:57.505
are you backing out?

00:39:00.025 --> 00:39:01.705
How can you call this backing out?

00:39:01.785 --> 00:39:05.185
This is getting back to where we belong
and doing our part.

00:39:05.265 --> 00:39:06.585
Getting back is backing out.

00:39:08.505 --> 00:39:10.985
We've taken a beating over a missing case
that hasn't even been filed.

00:39:11.065 --> 00:39:13.625
And now you say don't back out,
tell me how we move forward.

00:39:14.665 --> 00:39:16.745
Besides, we had an agreement
with Captain Feng.

00:39:16.825 --> 00:39:19.825
Today's the third day.
We have to keep our word.

00:39:20.745 --> 00:39:21.665
We still have tonight.

00:39:22.665 --> 00:39:25.185
Ran Fangxu, are you stupid or what?

00:39:26.145 --> 00:39:28.065
The task force has brought in Wu Shanlong.

00:39:28.145 --> 00:39:30.145
If you don't report in now,
forget the credit,

00:39:30.225 --> 00:39:31.745
you won't even get a shred of it.

00:39:31.825 --> 00:39:34.025
I didn't become a cop for credit.

00:39:34.105 --> 00:39:36.585
I owe Xu Meng and her dad the truth.

00:39:51.345 --> 00:39:54.145
He, after everything we've done,

00:39:54.905 --> 00:39:57.545
if we pull out now,
it'll all be for nothing.

00:39:58.065 --> 00:39:59.305
Let me tell you this.

00:40:00.745 --> 00:40:03.985
I've lived long enough to learn one thing.

00:40:04.585 --> 00:40:06.025
Don't get too hung up on things.

00:40:06.105 --> 00:40:07.945
Let go when you can.

00:40:08.025 --> 00:40:10.585
Or else, you'll drive yourself crazy.

00:40:28.065 --> 00:40:30.225
Looks like my first case

00:40:31.465 --> 00:40:32.825
is going to end in failure.

00:40:40.545 --> 00:40:42.785
Ever since I entered PPSUC,

00:40:43.545 --> 00:40:45.785
I've been studying all kinds
of missing person cases.

00:40:47.945 --> 00:40:49.305
I told myself that once
I became a police officer

00:40:50.105 --> 00:40:51.745
and took on a case,

00:40:51.825 --> 00:40:54.225
I'd find the missing person at all costs

00:40:55.385 --> 00:40:56.945
and leave no regrets.

00:41:01.185 --> 00:41:03.945
I thought I knew my stuff.

00:41:04.545 --> 00:41:06.185
But when it comes to real fieldwork,

00:41:08.665 --> 00:41:09.625
I'm nothing.

00:41:22.105 --> 00:41:23.105
That's funny.

00:41:24.185 --> 00:41:25.225
You know what?

00:41:26.545 --> 00:41:28.625
My first case
was a missing persons case too.

00:41:28.705 --> 00:41:31.265
It was an old man with dementia.

00:41:32.225 --> 00:41:33.785
I ran around for days,

00:41:33.865 --> 00:41:35.585
nearly wore my shoes out.

00:41:39.705 --> 00:41:40.985
So you failed too?

00:41:44.905 --> 00:41:46.105
I ran out of leads

00:41:46.905 --> 00:41:47.905
and had to try something stupid.

00:42:01.625 --> 00:42:02.985
Enough with the suspense.

00:42:04.065 --> 00:42:05.505
No. It's not that.

00:42:06.945 --> 00:42:07.825
Here's what I did.

00:42:08.665 --> 00:42:11.225
I pretended to be the old man

00:42:11.305 --> 00:42:14.025
and followed his way of thinking.

00:42:14.105 --> 00:42:14.985
I wandered around aimlessly.

00:42:15.065 --> 00:42:17.465
When I was hungry,
I grabbed whatever I could find.

00:42:17.545 --> 00:42:18.865
When I needed to pee,

00:42:18.945 --> 00:42:20.105
I just went wherever.

00:42:21.585 --> 00:42:22.465
And in the end,

00:42:22.545 --> 00:42:24.625
I actually found him.

00:42:28.465 --> 00:42:29.905
He.

00:42:29.985 --> 00:42:31.905
That's basically immersive roleplay.

00:42:34.385 --> 00:42:36.185
Yeah. Right.

00:42:37.785 --> 00:42:38.705
I came up with this myself

00:42:39.825 --> 00:42:41.465
22 years before you.

00:42:46.425 --> 00:42:49.345
How about we…

00:42:55.185 --> 00:42:56.465
No way.

00:42:59.505 --> 00:43:00.865
Listen.

00:43:00.945 --> 00:43:02.225
If you want to do that, go ahead.

00:43:02.305 --> 00:43:04.425
Anyone who goes with you
is out of their mind.

00:43:10.065 --> 00:43:11.065
NOTEBOOK

00:43:47.985 --> 00:43:49.865
Can you not breathe all over me?

00:43:49.945 --> 00:43:50.985
What?

00:43:51.505 --> 00:43:54.425
That old man in the footage
kept his head down like this.

00:43:55.505 --> 00:43:57.345
You smell like garlic.

00:43:57.425 --> 00:43:59.425
Focus on your job.

00:44:18.065 --> 00:44:20.465
Focus on your job. Lean back.

00:44:20.545 --> 00:44:21.905
You're getting back at me.

00:44:38.465 --> 00:44:40.305
Why are your legs shaking?

00:44:40.385 --> 00:44:42.545
You should lose some weight.

00:44:42.625 --> 00:44:43.825
If you can't handle it, I'll switch.

00:44:43.905 --> 00:44:45.305
Don't move.

00:44:45.385 --> 00:44:47.545
If we can't get it right this time,
we run it again.

00:44:52.545 --> 00:44:54.425
-I'm taking my jacket off.
-Steady.

00:45:04.825 --> 00:45:05.945
PRIVATE ROOM 1

00:45:06.985 --> 00:45:07.985
Hey.

00:45:08.065 --> 00:45:10.265
Have you picked up anything so far?

00:45:10.985 --> 00:45:11.905
No.

00:45:12.425 --> 00:45:14.945
Have you felt anything back there?

00:45:15.705 --> 00:45:16.705
I have.

00:45:17.465 --> 00:45:18.345
What is it?

00:45:18.425 --> 00:45:20.505
Xu Meng has better stamina than you.

00:45:29.065 --> 00:45:30.145
I may not have gone to the Police Academy,

00:45:30.865 --> 00:45:33.065
but I've been a cop for 22 years.

00:45:33.145 --> 00:45:35.265
I have my own ways of working things out.

00:45:35.865 --> 00:45:36.785
Let's hear it.

00:45:37.625 --> 00:45:40.025
Everything is always changing.
We only have so much energy.

00:45:40.105 --> 00:45:41.505
Focus on the big picture.
Don't dwell on the small stuff.

00:45:41.585 --> 00:45:43.145
Dress well, eat well.

00:45:43.745 --> 00:45:44.625
I understand the first three.

00:45:45.305 --> 00:45:46.945
What's that last one supposed to mean?

00:45:47.465 --> 00:45:50.345
Simple. What can't you live without?

00:45:50.425 --> 00:45:51.705
Eat, drink, sleep, and poop.

00:45:51.785 --> 00:45:53.265
It's in those everyday things

00:45:53.345 --> 00:45:54.785
that people slip up and leave traces.

00:45:54.865 --> 00:45:56.745
Take this cola.

00:45:56.825 --> 00:45:59.065
You pop it open, and it sprays everywhere.
You shake it off, right?

00:45:59.145 --> 00:46:02.985
And when you do, you leave a trail. Right?

00:46:05.185 --> 00:46:06.265
What are you looking at?

00:46:06.345 --> 00:46:08.985
He. Look. What's that?

00:46:11.945 --> 00:46:14.585
Isn't that where I shook off
the cola last time?

00:46:14.665 --> 00:46:15.785
No.

00:46:15.865 --> 00:46:17.585
Look higher. Up there.

00:46:25.705 --> 00:46:26.865
In the CCTV,

00:46:26.945 --> 00:46:29.105
Xu Meng's dad was holding a cigarette.

00:46:29.185 --> 00:46:30.465
He has a lung condition.

00:46:30.545 --> 00:46:31.865
Why would he be smoking?

00:47:14.865 --> 00:47:16.745
Easy. Stay calm.